text: Longeault-Pluvault is a commune in the Côte-d'Or department in eastern France. It was established on 1 January 2019 by merger of the former communes of Longeault (the seat) and Pluvault.Arrêté préfectoral 28 September 2018 ==See also== *Communes of the Côte-d'Or department ==References== Category:Communes of Côte-d'Or Category:Populated places established in 2019
title: Longeault-Pluvault
